asset.hookText:
Hi Dancer: We saw your review on our site. We're really happy to read you love your vacuum. Sometimes we've seen people have an issue with the dirt cup opening up when it's not clicked in all the way. We put together a quick video to help. If that doesn't fix your problem, let us know. We want to make sure it's working properly! -Felicia


Link for cyclone skirt video:  http://youtu.be/eLA0lQ3ywjM
